      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？　なんで私がこんなダサいTシャツ着て\n動画に出なきゃいけないのよ！　ありえないんだけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8999993085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.2730834722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "仕方がないでしょう。沙季からの誕生日プレゼントが\nこのいつも着ている、ダサいTシャツだったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4666659752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.5395684321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "プレゼントを受け取るところを動画に撮ってしまったし\nなんなら、貴方とお揃いだってことも話しているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0333326418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.0673005502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "いや確かにコメントで「お揃いなんだ～、いつか二人が\n着てるの見てみた～い」とか言われそうだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8333326418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "Tシャツ着るだけとか、ほんとに見たいのかしら……\nそもそもそんな動画、お蔵入りにすればいいでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7666659752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.7640576761
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "沙季と撮った動画なら、もうアップしたわ\n誕生日の動画だもの。今日中じゃないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2999993085,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3920.000000000002,
          "startTime": 54.2199993085
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10466.6666667,
          "startTime": 60.7666659752
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.4245340428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？　嘘でしょ、うわほんとにアップされてる！\nてか誕生日って誰の！　と、とにかく確認しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5999993085,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10551.362153,
          "startTime": 69.1513614615
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.3666659752
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0453043701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん、お誕生日おめでとうございます！\nこれ、つまらないものですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7999998331,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3761.8854364999947,
          "startTime": 72.5618852696
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。沙季の好きなキャラクターのTシャツね\nとっても可愛いわ。ぐっにゃいって言うのね、可愛い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9906834683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、以前franさんにも同じものをあげたんです\n嬉しかったのか、その場で気を失ってしまったくらいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4999998331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、私も気を失ってしまいそうなくらい嬉しいわ\n今度、二人で着てみるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2767823297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.2396847805
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.2396847805
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.1767823297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "――いやあんたの誕生日かい！！\nていうか動画の中で着るって言っちゃってるじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8101156631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.0653539738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "話の流れよ。あと私も被害者だから\nkanaに、ここカットしろって言っておいたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4101156631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.0553537132
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あのクソガキ……！　どうせカットし忘れたふりして\nさらっとアップロードしたんだわ。はぁ、最悪……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2101156631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.7093674105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "もう後戻り出来ないわ。天才パリコレモデルなら\nクソダサTシャツも着こなしてみせなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1101156631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.6870769263
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.9101156631
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.7767823297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないわね……ってなるか！！　そもそも私\nあれ寝間着にしてるのよ？　汚れてるかもしれないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9101156631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.7470766784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "普段から着ているならいいじゃない。三人のチャンネル\nなのだから、少しは協力してちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7434489964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.6283237538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "三人……そうよ、私達二人だけっておかしくない？\nいくらバズったとしても、私達だけ苦労するって変よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8101156631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 155.1371901275
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、kanaにも同じ服、買ってこない？\nあのSNS中毒が、動画の中で恥かくとか見ものだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9434489964,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13329.999999999984,
          "startTime": 172.2734489964
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 164.1897525233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_53_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "確かに。なら購入とkanaへの説明頼むわね。それが\nプレゼントがわりでいいわ。じゃあ私、撮影があるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4767823297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
